{"tid":1366343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[全民頭盔]有少少建議","createTime":"2019-07-26T02:33:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:58:50.000Z","uid":267678,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5548e54f4c276fbb8dcddecd3484d00acc165283","tid":1366343,"uid":267678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:33:14.000Z","msg":"- 戴得出街就代表緊抗爭者，所以面對挑釁要小心，用自己嘅方法處理(不割蓆，各有各做)，但係千祈唔好失控<br />\n- 絕對鼓勵戴住做義舉，例如扶阿婆過馬路，唔使勉強，自行決定<br />\n- 要有準備俾人問問題，例如「你有冇收錢」「你支持緊啲乜嘢」「個修訂你有咩唔滿意」，唔好俾人問到口啞啞，尤其五大訴求<br />\n- 唔一定要戴喺頭，掛喺袋度都好型嘅(fat唇嘅嘢)<br />\n- 裝飾少不免，不過太搶眼就唔好發夢都拎埋出嚟啦<br />\n- 元天屯高危地區呢排都唔建議咁做，我哋明嘅<br />\n- 做中資/藍絲公司嘅，準備定個袋裝住佢<br />\n- 有人建議戴到月尾，我自己就諗住一直戴到運動完結，大家睇情況啦<br />\n<br />\n令戴頭盔出街變成日常<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aaDBHxU\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aaDBHxU</a><br />\n<br />\n今日已經見到有人戴頭盔返工！唔好俾佢停！香港人要保護好自己！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aazkkCU\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aazkkCU</a><br />\n<br />\n全民頭盔月<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1343516\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1343516</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7VU37d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7VU37d.png&h=37389333&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/izSTU2A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FizSTU2A.png&h=b34c977c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JGGQXVv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJGGQXVv.png&h=472c3c93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MmOjRaR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMmOjRaR.jpg&h=fb545846&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NK8jTtx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNK8jTtx.png&h=3a1e8037&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wAui62x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%